0:16:38.26,000 --> 0:16:41,000
and by just doing simple things, doing the auction,

344
0:16:42.02,000 --> 0:16:43,000
changing some policies,

345
0:16:43.54,000 --> 0:16:45,000
we were able to bring the cost down.

