0:17:11.02,000 --> 0:17:12,000
in less than an hour.

357
0:17:12.58,000 --> 0:17:13,000
So we save lives,

358
0:17:14.06,000 --> 0:17:15,000
this program saved lives --

359
0:17:15.939,000 --> 0:17:16,000
(Applause)

360
0:17:16.98,000 --> 0:17:17,000
This program made money for Zipline

361
0:17:18.74,000 --> 0:17:22,000
and this program saved huge amounts of money for Rwanda.

362
0:17:22.78,000 --> 0:17:24,000
That's what we need, and we need that from all of you.

363
0:17:25.5,000 --> 0:17:28,000
I'm asking you, carve out a little bit of time in your brains

