0:19:08.06,000 --> 0:19:1,000
The future "you" -- and especially for your children --

404
0:19:10.82,000 --> 0:19:11,000
the future you

405
0:19:12.42,000 --> 0:19:14,000
will depend on how much care and compassion we bring

406
0:19:15.42,000 --> 0:19:19,000
to ensuring that the future "us" provides equality of opportunity

407
0:19:20.06,000 --> 0:19:21,000
for every child in the world.

408
0:19:21.5,000 --> 0:19:22,000
Thank you very much.

